    "There were more mistakes between the two extremes than with sentiment analysis training set (see S1 File for sentiment confusion matrix).",
    "We confirmed sentiment analysis training set performance by comparing the sentiment and stance predictions for all of the immigration related sentences, resulting in a fair agreement (kappa 0.29).",
